title: Galaxy Tab S9 FE Review
description:
NEW COURSES: http://bradsartschool.com

The Galaxy Tab line of tablets are my go to android tablet for drawing. This new S9 FE takes a lot of what I loved about the big brothers and it takes away some features to make it more budget priced and that's where it excels.
